Guang Zhou ESG New Energy Technology LTD is a sister company of Guangzhou Hengda Battery Co. Ltd all of which belong to the ESG POWER systems group, established back in 1988. Located in Panyu District, Guangzhou City on an area of about 80,000 square meters the company is mainly involved in the research, development, design, and manufacture, and sales and services of battery and solar systems. The companyâ€™s products, in particular, include solar panel, solar energy support, solar energy system, controller, inverter, battery, wind turbine, street lamp, solar water pump, uninterruptible power supply systems (UPS), power plant and substation switch control solar off-grid system, solar on-grid system and solar accessories among others. ESG sales network covers all provinces, municipalities, and autonomous regions in the people republic of china and the company has also established branch offices in various places and after-sales service centers. Furthermore, ESG holds an international trade certificate hence it exports its products to countries such as Japan, South Korea, the United States, Europe, Australia, Africa, and other regions. The company has also passed several quality certificates including the ISO9001 quality management system, the 2000 Quality System certification, the Guangdong Provincial Quality System Certification, Norske Veritas (DNV) ISO9001 quality system certification, the United States UL product safety certification, EU CE certification, etc. This is with no doubt a proof that ESG products are of high quality and are accepted in every corner of the world.